{
    "name": "Gluttonous Geode",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Gluttonous Geode",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Gluttonous geodes form when natural forces crack open a geode that's steeped in elemental magic, causing a natural break that acts like a hinged jaw. Though seemingly unimportant and no larger than a common turtle, gluttonous geodes are bellicose and dogged in their pursuit of an enemy.",
